939,Eddylevel,2018-04-30,4.0,"Second visit I first stayed in this hotel back in the winter, as a sort of insurance against snowy roads stopping me from catching my flight. This time we stayed simply for the convenience of just having to make a short journey across the road to Departures. It‚Äôs clean and reasonably comfortable if not offering the most spacious of rooms, and we found it very quiet and restful. That‚Äôs about as much as can be said for it - it‚Äôs convenient and no more, you certainly wouldn‚Äôt want to stay there for a pleasurable break!"
