2775,CRICKLEWOOD,2007-05-31,4.0,"Even better if your room is at the back Location ‚Äì Near temple Meads & opposite the new Rivergate Development incorporating Bristol & West. RBS  etc. The hotel faces a very busy road but backs on to a churchyard ‚Äì so select your bedroom with care. 

